In the Matter of Manuel ASENSIO, Appellant,
v.
Lawrence J. MARKS, etc., Respondent. (AD No. O.P. 130/2017) 2018-143 Court of Appeals of New York. February 15, 2018 On the Court's own motion, appeal dismissed, without costs, upon the ground that no substantial constitutional question is directly involved. Motion for leave to appeal denied. Chief Judge DiFiore took no part.
